 ABBA 的 Bjorn Ulvaeus 表示该乐队可能永远不会再一起出现在公共场合https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-bjorn-ulvaeus-may-never-appear-in-public-together-again-3767803?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=abba-bjorn-ulvaeus-may-再也不会一起出现在公共场合Surej SinghSat, 22 Jun 2024 09:11:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3767803 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="ABBA四位成员" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该团体最后一次公开团聚是在本月早些时候，并获得了瑞典爵士称号</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-bjorn-ulvaeus-may-never-appear-in-public-together-again-3767803">ABBA 的 Bjorn Ulvaeus 表示该乐队可能永远不会再一起公开露面，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="ABBA四位成员" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/abba@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>比约恩·乌尔瓦乌斯 (Bjorn Ulvaeus) 表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>可能再也不会一起公开露面了。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-bjorn-ulvaeus-on-the-future-of-the-voyage-live-show-and-if-theyd-ever-play-glastonbury-3432105">ABBA 的 Björn Ulvaeus 谈论“Voyage”现场表演的未来以及他们是否会参加格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月早些时候，瑞典流行偶像齐聚一堂，进行了一次罕见的公开露面，他们被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-reunite-to-be-honoured-with-swedish-knighthoods-3761627">授予瑞典皇家瓦萨勋章</a>。在<em>Rosebud With Gyles Brandreth</em>播客的一次新聊天中，Ulvaeus 透露这可能是他们的最后一次聊天。</p><p>在谈到这一荣誉时，乌尔瓦乌斯透露，他和他的乐队成员已经悄悄地意识到，这可能是所有四名成员一起外出活动的“最后一次”。 “我们静静地站在那里，从国王手中接过它，他说了几句话，这是一个非常安静、非常优雅的仪式。我们四个人当然都在那里。” </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：Björn Ulvaeus - ABBA 传奇" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/5pGe52U5FTkJSlZ6LTn6Qu?si=oQEQj7BFRYec1jpcwbgBEA&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>当主持人盖尔斯·布兰德雷斯 (Gyles Brandreth) 问及大家是否经常见面时，乌尔瓦乌斯回答道：“很少在公共场合见面，弗里达 (Lyngstad) 事后对我说，‘这可能是最后一次见面。’”非常难过，事后我想到了这一点，但我们已经不再年轻了。”</p><p>布兰德雷斯补充道，“你的同事有时会这么说，但他们并不一定是这个意思，”乌尔瓦乌斯说道：“我希望不是这样，这非常令人难过。”</p><p> Ulvaeus 发表此番言论之前，该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abbas-bjorn-ulvaeus-on-the-future-of-the-voyage-live-show-and-if-theyd-ever-play-glastonbury-3432105">去年在接受<em>NME</em>采访时谈到了他们对虚拟音乐会<em>ABBA Voyage</em>的未来计划</a>。一旦演出于 2026 年在伦敦结束，该集团希望将<em>ABBA Voyage</em>带到世界其他地区，包括亚洲、澳大利亚、北美。 </p><figure id="attachment_3614284" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3614284" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3614284" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="阿巴" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/ABBA-Photo-by-Olle-LINDEBORG-_-TT-News-Agency-_-AFP-_-Sweden-OUT-Photo-credit-should-read-OLLE-LINDEBORG_AFP-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3614284" class="wp-caption-text"> ABBA – 图片来源：OLLE LINDEBORG/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>乐队的最后一首新音乐出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/abba-voyage-review-3086633">2021 年随附的“Voyage”专辑</a>中，其中包含<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/abba-new-songs-i-still-have-faith-in-you-dont-shut-me-down-review-3036793">最近的两首单曲</a>“I Still Have Faith In You”和“Don&#39;t Shut Me Down”。当被问及乐队是否希望推出更多新音乐时，乌尔瓦厄斯说：“不，《Voyage》这张专辑是你听到我们的最后一张专辑”——但他确实对乐队回归的想法持开放态度对于更多像现场表演这样的项目，充分利用新兴技术。</p><p> “未来将会出现令人兴奋的新形式，但我们目前对此知之甚少，”他补充道。 “人工智能，虚拟宇宙，ABBA 也可能会参与到许多有趣且令人兴奋的创造性事情中。”</p><p>上个月（5 月 27 日），Ulvaeus 和 Benny Andersson 在庆祝<em>ABBA Voyage</em>两周年之夜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-tease-the-one-way-they-could-appear-at-glastonbury-3760123">参加了问答环节</a>。两位 ABBA 成员接受了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-voyage-live-house-band-who-are-they-how-long-perform-interview-3236008">Voyage 现场乐队</a>在格拉斯顿伯里表演的想法。 “哦是的！这是一个绝妙的主意，”乌尔瓦乌斯说。他们是一支很棒的乐队，为什么不让他们演奏呢？” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="ABBA 谈论他们的 Voyage 现场表演、新音乐以及下一步发展" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TVZ3SPkWObo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>德克萨斯州的莎琳·斯皮特里 (Sharleen Spiteri) 问二人是否考虑过在 Voyage 演出期间登上舞台与乐队一起演奏，安德森回答道：“当然。也许如果他们演奏格拉斯顿伯里音乐节并需要一名额外的钢琴演奏家……”</p><p> <em>ABBA Voyage</em>持续到 2026 年。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fabba-voyage-tickets%2Fartist%2F5358174">请访问此处</a>获取门票和更多信息。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/abba-bjorn-ulvaeus-may-never-appear-in-public-together-again-3767803">ABBA 的 Bjorn Ulvaeus 表示该乐队可能永远不会再一起公开露面，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
