”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezers-rivers-cuomo-talks-working-with-taylor-swift-and-being-hailed-her-musical-hero-3767767">韦泽 (Weezer) 的里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 谈论与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的合作并被誉为她的“音乐英雄”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 2009 年乐队英雄广告幕后花絮。图片来源：Charley Gallay 和 Kevin Winter via GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Weezer">韦泽</a>的<a href="/artists/Rivers-Cuomo">里弗斯·科莫</a>公开了他与<a href="/artists/Taylor-Swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>合作拍摄广告的经历，她称赞他是她的“音乐英雄”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-weezer-rivers-cuomo-3765447">Weezer 的 Rivers Cuomo：“如果泰勒·斯威夫特想要制作一张摇滚专辑，我很乐意帮忙！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>科莫<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-weezer-rivers-cuomo-3765447">在本周的<em>《摇滚杀死脑细胞》</em>系列节目中接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，回顾了 2009 年与这位《宝石迷阵》歌手的合作。这则广告是为电子游戏《乐队英雄》拍摄的，其中包括科莫、斯威夫特、《<a href="/artists/Fall-Out-Boy">打倒》</a>等。 <a href="/artists/Fall-Out-Boy">Boy</a>乐队的<a href="/artists/Pete-Wentz">Pete Wentz</a>和<a href="/artists/Blink-182">Blink-182</a>乐队的<a href="/artists/Travis-Barker">Travis Barker</a>重现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tom-cruise">汤姆·克鲁斯</a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2UVsyVLLcE">1983 年<em>电影《Risky Business</em> 》中标志性的“旧时光摇滚”舞蹈场景，</a>然后乐队开始表演斯威夫特 2008 年的热门歌曲“Love Story”。</p><p> “电影<em>《危险生意》</em>上映时我还是个十几岁的孩子，所以汤姆·克鲁斯穿着内衣跳舞的场景对我们这一代人来说是标志性的和有影响力的，所以能够与其他几位巨星一起重现这个场景是一种巨大的荣幸， “巴迪·霍利”歌手说道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特乐队英雄广告" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vHBcGG_9HBk?start=18&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="危险的商业舞蹈场景" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G2UVsyVLLcE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“泰勒·斯威夫特非常和蔼可亲，当她走进房间并开始与我们交谈时，每个人都爱上了她。她就像一个天生的领导者。”</p><p>在一次幕后视频采访中谈到广告的创作时，斯威夫特说道：“广告的前提是我们滑进客厅，里面有我和另外三名玩家，另外三名玩家是我的一些音乐英雄。所以当我得知来自 Weezer 的 Travis Barker、Pete Wentz 和 Rivers 正在随着我的歌曲演奏并真正摇滚起来时，我有点害怕。”</p><p>在斯威夫特称赞科莫是她的音乐英雄之一后， <em>《NME》</em>问科莫是否曾讨论过与斯威夫特的合作，科莫回答说：“不，我们从未谈论过这一点。我从来没有想到过这一点。如果她想制作一张摇滚专辑，我很乐意帮忙！我有预感，我会先接到<a href="/artists/Miley-Cyrus">麦莉赛勒斯</a>的电话！ [笑]那就太酷了。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特、特拉维斯·巴克、皮特·温兹和里弗斯·科莫 - BANDHERO" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LTSh48b1uXo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，Weezer 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezer-reflect-on-30th-anniversary-of-the-blue-album-and-share-original-home-demos-3755348">回顾了《蓝色专辑》30 周年并分享了原创的家庭演示</a>。</p><p>今年晚些时候，乐队将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezer-to-celebrate-30-years-of-debut-album-with-voyage-to-the-blue-planet-tour-with-flaming-lips-and-dinosaur-jr-3599743">开始他们即将到来的“蓝色星球之旅”北美巡演</a>。维泽将在演出中完整播放该唱片，并承诺将提供稀有品和“非常特别的嘉宾”。他们将得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-flaming-lips">The Flaming Lips</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dinosaur-jr">Dinosaur Jr.</a>的支持。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fweezer-tickets%2Fartist%2F766591" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找剩余的门票。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-what-weezer-and-smashing-pumpkins-played-as-they-kicked-off-their-joint-uk-tour-in-birmingham-3763815">Smashing Pumpkins 和 Weezer 本月早些时候在伯明翰开始了他们的联合英国巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezers-rivers-cuomo-talks-working-with-taylor-swift-and-being-hailed-her-musical-hero-3767767">韦泽 (Weezer) 的里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 谈论与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的合作并被誉为她的“音乐英雄”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
